The IPL Dashboard provides a clear and interactive summary of match outcomes, team performances, toss results, venues, seasons, and head-to-head comparisons from 2008‚Äì2024.
Using cleaned and standardized data, pivot tables, KPI cards, and slicers, the dashboard allows users to quickly explore:

Overall match trends across all seasons

Team-wise performance consistency

Toss decisions and their impact on match outcomes

Season-by-season variations in winning patterns

Venue-wise and city-wise match distribution

Head-to-head performance between any two teams

The automation added through VBA makes navigation smooth and enhances user interaction, turning raw match data into an accessible analytical tool.
